item.title: Morrisville State College
item.description: :: Learn in more than 70 specialized associate and bachelor degree programs with small class sizes and personal attention at Morrisville State College. Use pioneering technology with laptop and wireless initiatives and cutting-edge technology in academic labs. Access real world learning laboratories on campus. Have a great on-campus experience with student activities, clubs and organizations, residence hall activities and more.
